data.description: Oversized 3 car garage allows good space for the vehicles or storage BUT! Lets talk about the Basement and the storage it offers plus the opportunity to create more living space to suit your needs and currently offers finished rec room and half bath. This 4 bedroom, 3.1 bath home offers so many special surprises. When you enter the foyer you'll see the dining room to your right has served this family better by using it as the children's play room to your left of the foyer is the office space or use as a living room, several spaces in this home offer options to meet your needs. This bright kitchen is open to the family room with fireplace and a breakfast room that overlooks a large newer deck! Surprise on main level is a bedroom, a full bath & laundry room! Upstairs are 3 bedrooms 2 full baths and the owners suite has a second surprise! there is a charming room attached to the owners suite & currently serves as the nursery, could be an office or your choice! The owners have added so many important updates to this house in recent years: New HVAC 3/23, New deck 7/20, Roof replaced 6/22. Owners bath vanity and floor updated 7/22, Beautiful black Aluminum fence 7/22, Front porch railing 4/20, Window Blinds, thermostat, Nest doorbell, storm door and much more. Kitchen offers a 5 burner gas range, newer kitchen appliances will convey, washer and dryer do not. There is a whole house vacuum, radon mitigation system. Community pool, playground to enjoy! Location is so convenient to I-75, Austin Landing that offers shopping, entertainment and more!
